<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,254,677]" pageId="5" pageNumber="251">Description: Background colour yellow to light brown, numerous minute white spots present all over body except margins; marginal band white with greyish transversal stripes; dorsal longitudinal band speckled with interrupted brown and white blotches; pseudotentacles developed and square like, shaded with white and brown.</paragraph>
